    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s peak naturally aspirated era. Powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, it features six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp tactile feedback, sending power to the rear wheels via an M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis remains taut with reinforced rear subframe mounts, while the suspension maintains factory-spec damping and bushing integrity for precise turn-in. Finished with staggered Style 67 alloys, this is a driver\u2019s car optimized for performance and longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
